{"tid":1736811,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我係香港家長 我想攪個家長遊行","createTime":"2019-11-18T20:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:06:56.000Z","uid":176026,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ea12bf47c9bb276f042cd0461825ecce03573101","tid":1736811,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:27:15.000Z","msg":"借朋友account<br />\n<br />\n你好 我係香港嘅家長<br />\n我有兩個小朋友<br />\n我想攪個遊行 帶埋小朋友嘅遊行<br />\n主題係「停止使用化學武器」<br />\n*當然係促請政府回應5大訴求*<br />\n由於好多家長都擔心出面太多tg殘留物<br />\n好多細節希望可以集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n日期：11月23號 （星期六）<br />\n*手足果日有無行動？*<br />\n<br />\n地點：需要集思廣益<br />\n*唔好太多tg殘留物*<br />\n*家長們會擔心*<br />\n*要就腳*<br />\n<br />\n時間：1pm開始<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手諗下<br />\n我聽日就去申請不反<br />\n得家長 得天下<br />\n好多家長都想出一分力 <br />\n雖然唔可以獨留兒童在家中同大家夢中見<br />\n但願光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢發到屋企唔再幫手湊 欲出不能"},{"pid":"5b7cef45aa5527a69309a13ff4adde2a7a4f26dd","tid":1736811,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:27:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"543c4bfc63fffaed5106ced7f6cb8b276866bd13","tid":1736811,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:27:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa8d0b2dad6732ba03c08572975c8ad8fbc191db","tid":1736811,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:28:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef5906e4a7e1465f21b7c655c5b73ad71df9b627","tid":1736811,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:28:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"585385e56eaeb866b980929fa24cbef0e8cbdb05","tid":1736811,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:28:24.000Z","msg":"遊行有用一早贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04893bd7b0f477c98d9b4c8d2ee7e3cd55e3ad3","tid":1736811,"uid":176026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:28:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb18826930907fdf6813f9b115973091c09d7c42","tid":1736811,"uid"